'''Jand''' (also '''Jend'''), was a medieval town on the right bank of the lower [[Syr Darya|Jaxartes river]] in [[Transoxiana]]. It was the winter capital of [[Seljuk Empire|Seljuk]] power before their migration to Khurasan, and was ruined by the [[Mongols]], and is now a decayed village.
